{"tid":419404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獨木舟一星班","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T16:33:43.000Z","uid":72460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b33b5d77b86cacbb1b9d036c0066b56150577ac","tid":419404,"uid":72460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"報左康文署獨木舟一星班，想問除左防曬之外有D咩一定要帶去？點著衫最好？有咩要注意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6cb86ecc4c18f372b95137c3b8c40e3f50a677","tid":419404,"uid":58668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報左康文署獨木舟一星班，想問除左防曬之外有D咩一定要帶去？點著衫最好？有咩要注意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下你想玩到咩程度<br />\n基本一定會落水，所以窄身衫同長褲（過膝）<br />\n長褲係因為你會做一個叫hip fix既動作<br />\n唔著長褲初學者會好易磨損膝頭<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61d3f86c482438ddd39546ab840f55f3f96de03","tid":419404,"uid":8940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"記得著對白飯魚落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678fcf367dbfcbcf2c8291743a8cac52bcedbfa3","tid":419404,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"防曬最緊要啦"},{"pid":"686832845ae7c92257954391f2768fd2be40b4f4","tid":419404,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"5蚊銀"},{"pid":"bfe534890a9e2d94df0dd57d1aa8f5ed7fedb414","tid":419404,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"5蚊，防曬<br />\n衣著就跑步衫/快乾衫，長短袖睇你怕唔怕曬<br />\n褲短得啦，鞋新手神器白飯魚，不過入沙入到傻，出左海過一過水就冇事<br />\n帶支水/水樽，中場食飯/完場有得飲，曬左成日好需要水"},{"pid":"6d14b20faeae1910e51391f2955bccff54685271","tid":419404,"uid":72460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"有人話短褲，有人話長褲，我係咪應該著可以拉鏈長褲變短褲嗰d去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c93633f0856ef0e97098e3a0739d7a820623994","tid":419404,"uid":45262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"我都岩岩玩完一星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好玩"},{"pid":"4a7fb4d6e50a75f4fb92ce9db7f19dc52708756f","tid":419404,"uid":100526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"唔識游水玩唔玩得?"},{"pid":"4f816a1b6f69d15efdcda5b2dbfbdebee20f0c74","tid":419404,"uid":134350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識游水玩唔玩得?</blockquote><br />\n要識游五十米先可以玩考牌班"},{"pid":"664ada98f8a911c4e81b837b4166081b15174546","tid":419404,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識游水玩唔玩得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔怕水就得。因為你件助浮衣唔會比你沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53663d589c62bdf2a629dc7e9ae551ec11a55f40","tid":419404,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"有無人玩開K艇？ 一齊玩"}]}